svg.title: The seal of the University of California, Santa Cruz (UCSC)
svg.desc: This is the seal of the University of California, Santa Cruz (UCSC) ; it contains the following text: THE UNIVERSITY OF CALIFORNIA 1868 LET THERE BE LIGHT ; see http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:The_University_of_California_1868_UCSC.svg for more information.
